<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg</head><p>Der Rat übersendet Abschriften von Fehdebriefen, die am Matthiastag zugegangen sind, und bittet um Unterrichtung anderer Reichsstädte.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_17" id="7r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_17_r2l2">Augſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_17_r2l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> frewnde / vns ſind etlich entſagſbrief an ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l4">Matheis abent des <expan>ʒwelfbote<ex>n</ex></expan> nehſt vergangen ge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l5">antvvurtt worden / der wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> abſchrifft <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l6">hirẏnne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr das <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewrn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l7">vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freunden des Reichs Steten v̈mb ew / auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l8">alſo verkünden wöllet / daʒ ſie ſich darnach wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r2l9">cʒu richten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ciner<ex>is</ex></expan> Anno octauo </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_17" id="7r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Augspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> frewnde, uns sind etlich entsagsbrief an <app>
<note><q type="date">sant Matheis abent, des
                                        <expan>zwelfbote<ex>n</ex></expan> nehst
                                vergangen</q>25.02.1408</note>
</app>, geantwurtt worden, der wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> abschrifft <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hirynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>, und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewrn und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freunden, des reichs steten, ümb ew auch also
                        verkünden wöllet, daz sie sich darnach wissen czu richten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ciner<ex>is</ex></expan>
                        anno octavo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
